data.description: Charming 3-Bedroom Rustic Home on 7.20 AC M/L with Bonus Room, Outbuildings, Pavilion & Pool. Looking for a new home? This beautiful rustic home boasts 3 cozy bedrooms, 2 baths, and a bonus room – perfect for a growing family. Enjoy the beautiful hardwood floors and modern stainless steel appliances. Relax outside in the pavilion or take a dip in the pool. With cat screens on all windows and a porch that is covered and screened-in, you can savor the fresh air without worrying about pesky bugs. This delightful home is located on a cul-de-sac in close proximity to Lake Norfork. It has a total area of 1702 sq ft and is priced at $349,900.
